<h1><span id="Caro-Kann_Defence_-_Advance_Variation">Caro-Kann Defence - Advance Variation</span></h1>
<p>A sounder response than 4. Bd3, and more ambitious than 4. Nf3, 4. Nc3 has helped revitalize the Advance Variation of the Caro-Kann.
</p><p>It is almost always met with 4...e6, with black aiming ultimately to play c5.
</p>
<p><b>1.e4 c6 2.d4 d5 3.e5 Bf5 4.Nc3</b>
